@startuml
title SafetyValidation - Vehicle Signal Safety Enforcement (Pedestrian Excluded)

start

:Receive optimized phase-based timing plan;

:Validate minimum and maximum\nphase durations;
if (Phase duration valid?) then (Yes)
else (No)
    :Reject timing plan;
    stop
endif

:Check phase compatibility\n(no conflicting green movements);
if (No conflicts detected?) then (Yes)
else (No)
    :Reject timing plan;
    stop
endif

:Validate yellow and all-red\nclearance intervals;
if (Clearance intervals valid?) then (Yes)
else (No)
    :Reject timing plan;
    stop
endif

:Validate total cycle time\nwithin configured bounds;
if (Cycle time valid?) then (Yes)
else (No)
    :Reject timing plan;
    stop
endif

:Approve timing plan;
:Forward to deployment stage;

stop
@enduml
